Installation:

git clone git://github.com/gaoyangsandy/dotvim.git ~/.vim
ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
cd ~/.vim
git submodule init
git submodule update

Upgrade a plugin buddle:

cd ~/.vim/buddle/nerdtree
git pull origin master

Upgrade all bundled plugins:

cd ~/.vim
git submodule foreach git pull origin master


